    "display_name": "Treat Me",
    "long_instructions": "### Treat Me\r\n\r\n**Define:** *Treat Me* by Chlöe uses short, sharp sounds that create a **staccato** rhythm, like quick pops or steady heartbeats. Your challenge is to create a remix that emphasizes this staccato style using only 1- or 2-measure tracks from the song.\r\n\r\n**Prepare:** Explore the song and identify short tracks that have a punchy, rhythmic feel. Plan how you'll use loops to repeat those sounds and how you'll organize your code using a function. Listen to the example below to hear what this could sound like.\r\n\r\n**Try:** Choose at least 4 unique short tracks (1–2 measures). Use loops to repeat and layer your sounds. Organize your remix by placing part of your code in a function and calling it when needed.\r\n\r\n<div style=\"background:#ebe8f1; border: 0; border-radius: 10px; clear:both; padding: 5px\">\r\n\r\nNeed some help? Try the [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i> Docs](#clickable=documentation-button) in the upper-right corner!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n**Reflect:** Does your remix capture the staccato feel of the original? Do your loops and pauses help create that rhythmic energy? In order to complete this level, your remix must include:\r\n\r\n- At least 4 unique sounds\r\n- 3 loops\r\n- 1 function\r\n- At least 1 effect",
    "bubble_choice_description": "Treat Me by Chlöe has many quick 1 or 2 measure tracks that sound like quick pops of sound or steady heartbeats. Create a remix of the song that emphasizes these qualities",
    "thumbnail_url": "https://curriculum.code.org/media/musiclab/library-launch2024/packs/chloe_treat_me/chloe_treat_me.jpg",
